So `j₂ q₁ = ((Algebra.TensorProduct.assoc ℤ ℤ ℚ 𝓞 ZHat).symm : ℚ ⊗ 𝓞^ ≃ₐ[ℤ] D ⊗ ZHat).toAlgHom (Algebra.TensorProduct.includeRight q₁)`
